{"tid":604001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★急! $4000--新 iPad真的要來了？傳蘋果下週發表新品","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T12:46:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"16d7c5c83f429af97f07f4ce3b5fa839284b4945","tid":604001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"蘋果將於美國時間3/27日上午10點台灣時間為27日週二晚上11點）舉辦春季新品發表會，為搶攻教育市場版圖，推測將會發表平價版的 iPad 新機種。綜合多家外媒報導，近年來在全球教育市場領域，尤以Google 推出的 Chromebook、微軟推出的 Surface Laptop 筆電，訴求「高CP值的性價比」，取得市場佔有率優勢。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果為搶攻這塊流失多年的教育市場，將以旗下iPad 產品線為主力，並推出符合需求的平價版iPad，推測售價將可能會落在 260美元(約合台幣7,700元）左右；並有可能支援Apple Pencil觸控筆。另，也有消息傳出，蘋果還將會推出平價版的 MacBook Air 筆電，不過，發佈時間點預期會是在六月的WWDC開發者大會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/33279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F33279&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ed044755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F33279&h=99d7228f\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/33279</a>"},{"pid":"468f65009d66d4f549c9f6e976b962d80304a76f","tid":604001,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"這就是Apple<br />\n<br />\nsame as 2012 ipad3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24a0abce40ecc3c45f9eee26937bfbd6ede760c","tid":604001,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等緊8代u既macbook pro"},{"pid":"6fd584c584f29a0d446f04b7faa4a60d326c5af6","tid":604001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468f65009d66d4f549c9f6e976b962d80304a76f","tid":604001,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"這就是Apple<br />\n<br />\nsame as 2012 ipad3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c